oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Site of Parkway Terrace Apartments, n.d.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Photograph of the site of Parkway Terrace Apartments, (Project Tenn. 5-22) before their construction. The Nashville Housing Authority later purchased the 125-unit housing development from Henry Hudson Enterprises under the U.S. Department of Housing and Urban Development's turnkey program in 1971. Forms part of the MDHA Photograph Collection. 1 photograph : b & w.
